Luxx Studios bridges current and future digital technology to create VR and metaverse-ready experiences, real estate and wearables for a Cross-Platform experience. Our creators utilize the latest in augmented reality, blockchain, VR and game engines. Official Cryptolex Website https://cryptolex-nft.io/
